7f4457e3ca57b27c293136f8dce0c9d7dce21e01.query:
INSERT INTO counters (tenant_id, counter) VALUES ($1, 1)
            ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;

e675c3761e11c7b8eb7f5d93b8b9cc25e24299f4.query:
UPDATE counters
            SET counter = counter + $1
            FROM (
                     SELECT counter as prev
                     FROM counters
                     WHERE counters.tenant_id = $2
                     LIMIT 1
                 ) as c
            WHERE counters.tenant_id = $2
            RETURNING counter as new, c.prev
